{"tha-ap23:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap23:0.2":"Subhutivagga ","tha-ap23:0.3":"Subhutittheraapadana ","tha-ap23:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap23:1.2":"nisabho nama pabbato; ","tha-ap23:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap23:1.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap23:2.1":"Kosiyo nama namena, ","tha-ap23:2.2":"jatilo uggatapano; ","tha-ap23:2.3":"Ekakiyo adutiyo, ","tha-ap23:2.4":"vasami nisabhe tada. ","tha-ap23:3.1":"Phalam mulanca pannanca, ","tha-ap23:3.2":"na bhunjami aham tada; ","tha-ap23:3.3":"Pavattamva supataham, ","tha-ap23:3.4":"upajivami tavade. ","tha-ap23:4.1":"Naham kopemi ajivam, ","tha-ap23:4.2":"cajamanopi jivitam; ","tha-ap23:4.3":"Aradhemi sakam cittam, ","tha-ap23:4.4":"vivajjemi anesanam. ","tha-ap23:5.1":"Ragupasamhitam cittam, ","tha-ap23:5.2":"yada uppajjate mama; ","tha-ap23:5.3":"Sayamva paccavekkhami, ","tha-ap23:5.4":"ekaggo tam damemaham. ","tha-ap23:6.1":"‘Rajjase rajjaniye ca, ","tha-ap23:6.2":"dussaniye ca dussase; ","tha-ap23:6.3":"Muyhase mohaniye ca, ","tha-ap23:6.4":"nikkhamassu vana tuvam. ","tha-ap23:7.1":"Visuddhanam ayam vaso, ","tha-ap23:7.2":"nimmalanam tapassinam; ","tha-ap23:7.3":"Ma kho visuddham dusesi, ","tha-ap23:7.4":"nikkhamassu vana tuvam. ","tha-ap23:8.1":"Agariko bhavitvana, ","tha-ap23:8.2":"yada puttam labhissasi; ","tha-ap23:8.3":"Ubhopi ma viradhesi, ","tha-ap23:8.4":"nikkhamassu vana tuvam. ","tha-ap23:9.1":"Chavalatam yatha kattham, ","tha-ap23:9.2":"na kvaci kiccakarakam; ","tha-ap23:9.3":"Neva game aranne va, ","tha-ap23:9.4":"na hi tam katthasammatam. ","tha-ap23:10.1":"Chavalatupamo tvamsi, ","tha-ap23:10.2":"na gihi napi sannato; ","tha-ap23:10.3":"Ubhato muttako ajja, ","tha-ap23:10.4":"nikkhamassu vana tuvam. ","tha-ap23:11.1":"Siya nu kho tava etam, ","tha-ap23:11.2":"ko pajanati te idam; ","tha-ap23:11.3":"Saddhadhuram vahisi me, ","tha-ap23:11.4":"kosajjabahulaya ca. ","tha-ap23:12.1":"Jigucchissanti tam vinnu, ","tha-ap23:12.2":"asucim nagariko yatha; ","tha-ap23:12.3":"Akaddhitvana isayo, ","tha-ap23:12.4":"codayissanti tam sada. ","tha-ap23:13.1":"Tam vinnu pavadissanti, ","tha-ap23:13.2":"samatikkantasasanam; ","tha-ap23:13.3":"Samvasam alabhanto hi, ","tha-ap23:13.4":"katham jivihisi tuvam. ","tha-ap23:14.1":"Tidha pabhinnam matangam, ","tha-ap23:14.2":"kunjaram satthihayanam; ","tha-ap23:14.3":"Bali nago upagantva, ","tha-ap23:14.4":"yutha niharate gajam. ","tha-ap23:15.1":"Yutha vinissato santo, ","tha-ap23:15.2":"sukham satam na vindati; ","tha-ap23:15.3":"Dukkhito vimano hoti, ","tha-ap23:15.4":"pajjhayanto pavedhati. ","tha-ap23:16.1":"Tatheva jatila tampi, ","tha-ap23:16.2":"niharissanti dummatim; ","tha-ap23:16.3":"Tehi tvam nissato santo, ","tha-ap23:16.4":"sukham satam na lacchasi. ","tha-ap23:17.1":"Diva va yadi va rattim, ","tha-ap23:17.2":"sokasallasamappito; ","tha-ap23:17.3":"Dayhasi parilahena, ","tha-ap23:17.4":"gajo yuthava nissato. ","tha-ap23:18.1":"Jatarupam yatha kutam, ","tha-ap23:18.2":"neva jhayati katthaci; ","tha-ap23:18.3":"Tatha silavihino tvam, ","tha-ap23:18.4":"na jhayissasi katthaci. ","tha-ap23:19.1":"Agaram vasamanopi, ","tha-ap23:19.2":"katham jivihisi tuvam; ","tha-ap23:19.3":"Mattikam pettikancapi, ","tha-ap23:19.4":"natthi te nihitam dhanam. ","tha-ap23:20.1":"Sayam kammam karitvana, ","tha-ap23:20.2":"gatte sedam pamocayam; ","tha-ap23:20.3":"Evam jivihisi gehe, ","tha-ap23:20.4":"sadhu te tam na ruccati. ","tha-ap23:21.1":"Evaham tattha varemi, ","tha-ap23:21.2":"sankilesagatam manam; ","tha-ap23:21.3":"Nanadhammakatham katva, ","tha-ap23:21.4":"papa cittam nivarayim’. ","tha-ap23:22.1":"Evam me viharantassa, ","tha-ap23:22.2":"appamadaviharino; ","tha-ap23:22.3":"Timsavassasahassani, ","tha-ap23:22.4":"vipine me atikkamum. ","tha-ap23:23.1":"Appamadaratam disva, ","tha-ap23:23.2":"uttamattham gavesakam; ","tha-ap23:23.3":"Padumuttarasambuddho, ","tha-ap23:23.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap23:24.1":"Timbarusakavannabho, ","tha-ap23:24.2":"appameyyo anupamo; ","tha-ap23:24.3":"Rupenasadiso buddho, ","tha-ap23:24.4":"akase cankami tada. ","tha-ap23:25.1":"Suphullo salarajava, ","tha-ap23:25.2":"vijjuvabbhaghanantare; ","tha-ap23:25.3":"Nanenasadiso buddho, ","tha-ap23:25.4":"akase cankami tada. ","tha-ap23:26.1":"Siharajavasambhito, ","tha-ap23:26.2":"gajarajava dappito; ","tha-ap23:26.3":"Lasito byaggharajava, ","tha-ap23:26.4":"akase cankami tada. ","tha-ap23:27.1":"Singinikkhasavannabho, ","tha-ap23:27.2":"khadirangarasannibho; ","tha-ap23:27.3":"Mani yatha jotiraso, ","tha-ap23:27.4":"akase cankami tada. ","tha-ap23:28.1":"Visuddhakelasanibho, ","tha-ap23:28.2":"punnamayeva candima; ","tha-ap23:28.3":"Majjhanhikeva suriyo, ","tha-ap23:28.4":"akase cankami tada. ","tha-ap23:29.1":"Disva nabhe cankamantam, ","tha-ap23:29.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","tha-ap23:29.3":"‘Devo nu kho ayam satto, ","tha-ap23:29.4":"udahu manujo ayam. ","tha-ap23:30.1":"Na me suto va dittho va, ","tha-ap23:30.2":"mahiya ediso naro; ","tha-ap23:30.3":"Api mantapadam atthi, ","tha-ap23:30.4":"ayam sattha bhavissati’. ","tha-ap23:31.1":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap23:31.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap23:31.3":"Nanapupphanca gandhanca, ","tha-ap23:31.4":"sannipatesaham tada. ","tha-ap23:32.1":"Pupphasanam pannapetva, ","tha-ap23:32.2":"sadhucittam manoramam; ","tha-ap23:32.3":"Narasarathinam aggam, ","tha-ap23:32.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap23:33.1":"‘Idam me asanam vira, ","tha-ap23:33.2":"pannattam tavanucchavam; ","tha-ap23:33.3":"Hasayanto mamam cittam, ","tha-ap23:33.4":"nisida kusumasane’. ","tha-ap23:34.1":"Nisidi tattha bhagava, ","tha-ap23:34.2":"asambhitova kesari; ","tha-ap23:34.3":"Sattarattindivam buddho, ","tha-ap23:34.4":"pavare kusumasane. ","tha-ap23:35.1":"Namassamano atthasim, ","tha-ap23:35.2":"sattarattindivam aham; ","tha-ap23:35.3":"Vutthahitva samadhimha, ","tha-ap23:35.4":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap23:35.5":"Mama kammam pakittento, ","tha-ap23:35.6":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap23:36.1":"‘Bhavehi buddhanussatim, ","tha-ap23:36.2":"bhavananamanuttaram; ","tha-ap23:36.3":"Imam satim bhavayitva, ","tha-ap23:36.4":"purayissasi manasam. ","tha-ap23:37.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap23:37.2":"devaloke ramissasi; ","tha-ap23:37.3":"Asitikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap23:37.4":"devarajjam karissasi; ","tha-ap23:37.5":"Sahassakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap23:37.6":"raja ratthe bhavissasi. ","tha-ap23:38.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap23:38.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap23:38.3":"Anubhossasi tam sabbam, ","tha-ap23:38.4":"buddhanussatiya phalam. ","tha-ap23:39.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap23:39.2":"mahabhogam labhissasi; ","tha-ap23:39.3":"Bhoge te unata natthi, ","tha-ap23:39.4":"buddhanussatiya phalam. ","tha-ap23:40.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap23:40.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap23:40.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap23:40.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap23:41.1":"Asitikotim chaddetva, ","tha-ap23:41.2":"dase kammakare bahu; ","tha-ap23:41.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap23:41.4":"sasane pabbajissasi. ","tha-ap23:42.1":"Aradhayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap23:42.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap23:42.3":"Subhuti nama namena, ","tha-ap23:42.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap23:43.1":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap23:43.2":"dakkhineyyagunamhi tam; ","tha-ap23:43.3":"Tatharanavihare ca, ","tha-ap23:43.4":"dvisu agge thapessati’. ","tha-ap23:44.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap23:44.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap23:44.3":"Nabham abbhuggami viro, ","tha-ap23:44.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap23:45.1":"Sasito lokanathena, ","tha-ap23:45.2":"namassitva tathagatam; ","tha-ap23:45.3":"Sada bhavemi mudito, ","tha-ap23:45.4":"buddhanussatimuttamam. ","tha-ap23:46.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap23:46.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap23:46.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap23:46.4":"tavatimsam agacchaham. ","tha-ap23:47.1":"Asitikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap23:47.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap23:47.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap23:47.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap23:48.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap23:48.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap23:48.3":"Anubhomi susampattim, ","tha-ap23:48.4":"buddhanussatiya phalam. ","tha-ap23:49.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap23:49.2":"mahabhogam labhamaham; ","tha-ap23:49.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap23:49.4":"buddhanussatiya phalam. ","tha-ap23:50.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap23:50.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap23:50.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap23:50.4":"buddhanussatiya phalam. ","tha-ap23:51.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap23:51.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap23:51.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap23:51.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap23:52.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma subhuti thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap23:53.1":"Subhutittherassapadanam pathamam. "}